item.title: CVE-2024-6459|2024-08-17T06:00:02.718Z -- unknown -- news%20element%20elementor%20blog%20magazine
item.description: The News Element Elementor Blog Magazine WordPress plugin before 1.0.6 is vulnerable to Local File Inclusion via the template parameter. This makes it possible for unauthenticated attacker to include and execute PHP files on the server, allowing the execution of any PHP code in those files.
